c: 39
v: 38
t: "And truly, if you are to ask them: \"Who created the heavens and the earth?\" Surely, they would say, \"Allah.\" Say: \"Do you see then? The things that you invoke besides Allah— If Allah gives me some penalty, can they remove His penalty? Or if He gives some mercy for me, can they keep back His mercy from?\" Say: \"Sufficient is Allah for me! In Him trust those who put their trust"